{"tid":1490534,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大廈閉路電視片段所見 疑兇是拍卡進入嘉明閣大廈","createTime":"2019-08-20T06:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T07:25:55.000Z","uid":169676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6734b84232464eb91a9b91e3cd16462b4fe0f493","tid":1490534,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:44:28.000Z","msg":"將軍澳景林邨連接頌明苑及厚德邨行人隧道內「連儂牆」，今日凌晨（20日）發生中年漢斬傷3名男女案件。嘉明閣30樓住戶楊先生說，深夜聽到有嘈吵聲，往樓下察看發現有一名女子在拍攝短片，其間聽到有淒慘叫聲，並見施襲者往頌明苑A座嘉明閣方向逃走，於是下樓了解，楊先生下樓後見一名女傷者倒臥地上，不少穿黑衣的年輕人亦在場幫忙，未幾警員陸續到場調查，在頌明苑公園一個垃圾桶找到一把刀後離開，其間沒有翻查嘉明閣的閉路電視片段。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">約一小時後，有居民自發由嘉明閣35樓往下逐層搜索，並在21樓找到一件染血的淺藍色圓領短袖上衣，以及一條白點深藍色短褲，相信是疑兇犯案時所穿衣物。有居民報警，要求翻看大廈閉路電視片段。楊先生描述片段所見，疑兇是拍卡進入大廈，「好肯定是住戶，與看更打招呼，在升降機內行嚟行去」。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n嘉明閣大堂保安員稱，疑兇較早前將單位出租予內地大學生，到近來收回單位裝修</span>，近一個多月才見到疑兇出入，疑兇通常晚上8時許回來，並常與父親出入。他續說，疑兇平日「行路都要左望右望」，貌似以為有人在跟蹤自己，據保安員了解，疑兇在鄰座亦持有一單位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190820/s00001/1566277686591/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e5%98%89%e6%98%8e%e9%96%a3%e5%b1%85%e6%b0%91%e8%87%aa%e7%99%bc%e6%b4%97%e6%a8%93-%e6%aa%a2%e6%96%ac%e4%ba%ba%e7%96%91%e5%85%87%e8%a1%a3%e7%89%a9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190820%2Fs00001%2F1566277686591%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%2598%2589%25e6%2598%258e%25e9%2596%25a3%25e5%25b1%2585%25e6%25b0%2591%25e8%2587%25aa%25e7%2599%25bc%25e6%25b4%2597%25e6%25a8%2593-%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e6%2596%25ac%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e7%2596%2591%25e5%2585%2587%25e8%25a1%25a3%25e7%2589%25a9&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6VuajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=09ed20c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190820%2Fs00001%2F1566277686591%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%2598%2589%25e6%2598%258e%25e9%2596%25a3%25e5%25b1%2585%25e6%25b0%2591%25e8%2587%25aa%25e7%2599%25bc%25e6%25b4%2597%25e6%25a8%2593-%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e6%2596%25ac%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e7%2596%2591%25e5%2585%2587%25e8%25a1%25a3%25e7%2589%25a9&h=cd49a841\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190820/s00001/1566277686591/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e5%98%89%e6%98%8e%e9%96%a3%e5%b1%85%e6%b0%91%e8%87%aa%e7%99%bc%e6%b4%97%e6%a8%93-%e6%aa%a2%e6%96%ac%e4%ba%ba%e7%96%91%e5%85%87%e8%a1%a3%e7%89%a9</a>"},{"pid":"335024c6fed7867e68d8a2a654189d77bff76ec6","tid":1490534,"uid":253511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:46:12.000Z","msg":"與看更打招呼?????????????????????"},{"pid":"c5c3b18a54fab1d50be3f1de7852069952e3a225","tid":1490534,"uid":37463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:47:08.000Z","msg":"個保安冇得唔督佢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔係住戶 , 直接開門俾佢入=保安失職<br />\n如果係住戶 = 條藍屍冇撚得走"},{"pid":"1e9c9b854521803af6cde58e7ce8db9f2f06daaa","tid":1490534,"uid":223727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"條藍屍可能已經潛逃返左大陸"},{"pid":"464ade1a7b0130013c309aff8382fd70c6b2b48c","tid":1490534,"uid":149323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20